Package: d3tm
Title: A Zoomable Treemap Capable of Handling Unbalanced Hierarchical Data
Version: 0.4.2
Authors@R: c(person("Luke", "Heley", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "lajh87@me.com"))
Description: An R implementation of Mike Bostock's d3 treemap that supports 
    zooming: click any cell to zoom in, or the click the title bar to zoom out.
Imports: 
    htmlwidgets,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    callr,
    r2d3,
    shiny
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
URL: https://lajh87.github.io/d3tm/
BugReports: https://github.com/lajh87/d3tm/issues
